CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 30, 1960, pg. 20 reads: "Frogs Fete 'Teens' With Dancing Party at Loendi"
TitMainTitle: Group, including Aileen Eckstein Sawyer on left holding gifts to Mike Malone and Wanda, with Oscar Harris in center middle, and Leslie Smith, Toni Bray, and Daryl Smith towards left, in Loendi Club for FROGS teenage dance party
